                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7790" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1212</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1716 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">后疫情时代下山西戎子葡萄酒庄的 市场定位与营销策略之争</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Competition between Market Positioning and Strategy  of Shanxi Rongzi Winery in the Post Epidemic Era </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵杨，赵颖斯，赵振男</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山西戎子酒庄有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">22 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STP分析；会员营销；体验营销；客户关系管理系统；战略体验模型；个性化定制</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STP; members marketing; experiential marketing; Strategic Experiential Modules; CRM system; Personalized customization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">三年疫情，使得我国葡萄酒市场萎靡不振。同时，由于进口葡萄酒关税不断降低，我国葡萄酒市场面临“进口品牌攻城略地、国内巨头全方位对抗、中小品牌差异化竞争”的格局。在这个 “红海”市场中，地方性中小品牌举步维艰，本案例中的山西戎子酒庄就陷入了困境。为找到适合自身的发展路径，实现省外市场的突破，戎子酒庄决心重新进行市场定位，并据此进行营销策略的变革。在此过程中，面临着“精品定位，会员营销”与“全品定位，体验营销”两种不同的市场定位及营销策略的抉择，它们各有优劣，使酒庄决策者难以定夺。
本案例旨在启发学生认知关于企业市场定位的驱动因素以及营销变革策略的体系构建方法；引导学生树立“以消费者为中心”的营销理念；切实掌握会员营销与体验营销等营销新概念，据此构建具有实操性的营销方案。此外，戎子酒庄所面临的困境在我国中小地方性葡萄酒品牌中具有普遍性，因此，本案例所涉及的市场重新定位与营销策略变革可为同类企业的创新发展带来启发，也为我国国内葡萄酒中小品牌的健康成长提供了借鉴思路。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The red wine market in China is faced with the pattern of &quot;import brands to attack the city, the omni-directional confrontation of the domestic tycoons and the differentiation of other brands&quot;. In this condition, in order to find a strategy that is suitable for its own development, Shanxi Rongzi winery repositioned itself in the markets outside Shanxi province, and accordingly carried out corresponding marketing strategy reform. But in the process, it faces two options: &quot;experience marketing&quot; and &quot;members marketing&quot;. Each of them has advantages and disadvantages, making it difficult for wine makers to decide. The purpose of this case is to inspire students to recognize the driving force of market positioning and the strategy of marketing change, to guide students to grasp the important concepts in the marketing field of experience marketing and members marketing, and to build a practical marketing plan. In addition, this case can provide some inspiration for the innovation and development of similar enterprises, and also summarizes some marketing ideas for the growth of wine brands in China.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《企业战略管理》、《品牌管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STP分析；会员营销；体验营销；客户关系管理系统；战略体验模型；个性化定制</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
